oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ernest Tubb and his Texas Troubadours - That Wild And Wicked Look In Your Eye (live radio performance) / Ernest Tubb talks about the birth of his daughter
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Radio broadcast excerpt of a live Ernest Tubb and his Texas Troubadours performance of That Wild And Wicked Look In Your Eye (see also [ TR001838_1 ]). Followed by Ernest Tubb talking with "Judson" (likely Jud Collins) about the birth of his daughter, Erlene Dale Tubb, before starting a performance of Big Blue Diamonds - likely an excerpt from a Grand Ole Opry broadcast (unconfirmed) (see also [ TR001850_2 ]).
